195
00:07:38,879 --> 00:07:40,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ti si rekao, ne, ja nisam influencer,

196
00:07:40,980 --> 00:07:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] ja nisam samo content creator,

197
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:43,259
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam biznismen.

198
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:48,060
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ti temeljita osoba, znaš.

199
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,600
