207
00:08:02,019 --> 00:08:04,259
[SPEAKER_01] takav je pristup na prvu.

208
00:08:04,259 --> 00:08:05,459
[SPEAKER_01] Ti vidiš brojku

209
00:08:05,459 --> 00:08:08,100
