[SPEAKER_01] toliko i toliko ljudi prate,

220
00:08:25,139 --> 00:08:26,980
[SPEAKER_01] to je, ti si logično influencer.

221
00:08:26,980 --> 00:08:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim,

222
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] i to ne mogu zamjeriti

223
00:08:29,500 --> 00:08:31,240
[SPEAKER_01] na toj izjavi sve,

224
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja se uopće tako ne oslovljavam

225
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,620
[SPEAKER_01] i ne vidim se u tome.

226
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] I postoji, kad sam razmišljao,

227
00:08:36,659 --> 00:08:38,620
