228
00:08:38,620 --> 00:08:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] koji bi odgovor bio najbolji na to pitanje?

229
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:43,919
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se nisam osjećao ugodno

230
00:08:43,919 --> 00:08:45,799
