719
00:57:57,000 --> 00:57:59,500
[SPEAKER_01] Tak se zove knjiga.

720
00:57:59,500 --> 00:58:02,360
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da je čak neki, ono,

721
00:58:02,360 --> 00:58:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] u crno čovjek,

722
00:58:04,739 --> 00:58:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] da je neki kodaj pas tamo.

723
00:58:06,440 --> 00:58:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] To je, uglavnom, to je,

724
00:58:08,139 --> 00:58:09,780
[SPEAKER_01] kad me ovako pitaš,

725
00:58:09,780 --> 00:58:11,980
[SPEAKER_01] prva koja mi iskače

726
